Class JIPipeDataBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.nodes.JIPipeDataBatch

    public class JIPipeDataBatch
extends Object
implements Comparable<JIPipeDataBatch>
    Wraps a set of input and output slots that belong together This can be used for convenience
